p.k: After an excessive spending spree, the Golden Goose tells the gang it won't give them any more golden eggs until they learn the value of money. / Brock drags Master Frown along to join him in following his dream, to become the Flyer on a cheerleading team. / A super-grumpy volcano appears in the kingdom, so Unikitty takes the gang on an epic quest to cheer it up. / An asteroid is headed right for the kingdom, so Dr Fox leads the gang on a mission to save the kingdom. / It's time for the gang's yearly vacation, but Hawk refuses to go, claiming the gang's vacations are never fun for him.
